description.en:
Philanthropy Finance (PhiFi) is born from the necessity to create a healthier and balanced type of financial ecosystem. One where the profits are shared among its participants in a fair way; where the profits also are used to improve the world we live in.
- rewards holders in pegged BTC
- own community DEX
- Mobile App
- NFT charity marketplace
- DeFi Platform
- Donations (child) charities & adoption
- NFT charity marketplace & charity token (also for Bridge)
- Charity Bridge
- Constant development of new features related to market sentiment
